{"tid":1951405,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本攝影師紀錄香港抗爭前線：「讓更多人知道 年輕人們正在戰鬥。」","createTime":"2020-03-31T03:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T04:12:24.000Z","uid":161430,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44d75aaf07490bedaff97ddd52b357812c212cec","tid":1951405,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:19:00.000Z","msg":"日本TBS電視台的記錄片節目 (同為節目主題曲)。在剛剛3月30號播放的一集「從小主題中傳達的事」中，紀錄了日本知名獨立自由記者堀潤投身媒體行業的原因及當中的心路歷程。<br />\n<br />\n去年，他來港拍攝香港反修例示威的情況，並遇上了另一位日本女攝影師，Kiseki Michiko（キセキミチコ）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E4%B9%8B%E7%A9%BA-%E5%A0%80%E6%BD%A4-TBS%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E5%25A0%2580%25E6%25BD%25A4-TBS%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE-9.jpg&h=8f6f9bc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當Kiseki Michiko被問到拍攝香港反修例示威的最大理由是，她說：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「我想透過照片傳達香港的情況。讓更多人知道香港變成了現在的境況，年輕人他們正在戰鬥。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n她在示威中拍攝了不少照片卻無處發佈，她只可以在Twitter等個人專頁發佈：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kisekimichiko/status/1243878511535783936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkisekimichiko%2Fstatus%2F1243878511535783936&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtD%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=fdffffcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkisekimichiko%2Fstatus%2F1243878511535783936&h=8606a67e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kisekimichiko/status/1243878511535783936</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ESkaLbLU0AEvIPZ?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FESkaLbLU0AEvIPZ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=66f0f403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入去支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nKiseki Michiko（キセキミチコ）:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kisekimichiko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkisekimichiko&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtD%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=d5afe711\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kisekimichiko</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：日本TBS新聞節目 以詳細圖表清楚解釋香港反送中遊行發生原因"},{"pid":"6345bba604c643e35e822e8d21727fe3b92fdaf7","tid":1951405,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:19:27.000Z","msg":"開始日日都有還押幾個月手足上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1951351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1951351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"26e3c473b36cf3486fbd899df3a2ebfc73ec78dc","tid":1951405,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E4%B9%8B%E7%A9%BA-%E5%A0%80%E6%BD%A4-TBS%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E5%25A0%2580%25E6%25BD%25A4-TBS%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE-9.jpg&h=8f6f9bc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"285b29183ed1efb73f19ea2515287ffed0f6b883","tid":1951405,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:19:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1c55954a4f95fbdd830d682e7cb172176a96c78","tid":1951405,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfqRNPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfqRNPE.jpg&h=4eb21e8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fa427bd8215127a0908c4b0044043d87954aafe","tid":1951405,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited